Let's get started!
Foley has 3 products that help customers manage risk and stay up to date on what's going on with their compliance data and their fleet.
This includes, MVR Monitor, Audit Risk Monitor, and CSA Monitor.
Back of the flip card
MVR Monitor
Performs a daily review of all driver licenses for any updates or changes. This includes, speeding violations, DWI, license updates, and medical certificate downgrades. As a Foley customer get alerted as soon as a change is caught.
The data comes from the state licensing agency.
Back of the flip card
Audit Risk Monitor
A monthly compliance data wrap-up that includes CSA Measure, Foley Compliance Score, and score changes over time. It helps Foley customers keep up to date on their compliance health so they can act fast if their scores start to slip.
This data comes from within Foley Software and FMCSA BASIC data.
Back of the flip card
CSA Monitor
CSA Monitor gives you daily, real-time insights into your compliance scores and driver activity. It lets you know any time there is a violation, crash, or inspection to report with your fleet. You also get weekly trending data. Foley checks your FMCSA portal every single day and lets you know within 24 hours of any updates in the portal.
This data comes from the FMCSA Portal.
