Did you know that if companies use tools like Foley's data and monitoring products, they can lower their insurance premiums?!
Insurance premiums climb higher when compliance scores fall and when there are a lot of driver violations.

By having monitoring tools, they can go back to their insurance agents and prove that they are proactively managing risk.

This will help companies that hire drivers lower their risk, reduce costs by lowering insurance premiums, and also reduce their chances of being audited.
Customer Pain Points:
Too many drivers to keep track of and too much going on in the company
Lack of visibility into compliance and driver activity. This leads to getting notified too late about critical details of an incident
Manually tracking driver activity and compliance scores takes a long time and is difficult to prioritize
Our costs and Insurance premiums keep climbing due to unsafe driver behaviors. We don't know how to lower our insurance premiums
Incorrect reporting on our driver and company impacts our CSA Scores and cost of doing business.
