Getting started with CSA Monitor is simple for the customer.
All Foley needs is:
Driver DOT #s
Email addresses the CSA Monitor should send to.
Foley will ask for access to the customer's FMCSA Portal data. Once accepted, Foley automatically pulls driver activity and CSA data and reports back to the customer any time there are changes.

